{"tid":1229234,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"一首歌送畀身為香港人嘅你 加油撐住!! 《廿二年後的家》","createTime":"2019-06-16T00:38:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-16T06:58:37.000Z","uid":261040,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"5c36807b16eff6fe8e4d80befa05d99ce9501d36","tid":1229234,"uid":261040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T00:38:42.000Z","msg":"《廿二年後的家》<br />\n原曲: 二十年後的歌 - Dear Jane<br />\n<br />\n反送中的他　人生的曲折總會記得嗎<br />\n無恥惡警至想以民眾當槍靶<br />\n慈悲的哭喊都當作喧嘩<br />\n願我出言沒有怕<br />\n願我家遍開鮮花<br />\n願理想沒給壓榨<br />\n<br />\n准我唱首歌　和今天的你解脫了心鎖<br />\n回歸致失去的確實會有很多<br />\n而漆黑中卻總會有星火<br />\n讓抗爭除掉過錯<br />\n讓政府悔不當初<br />\n讓挽歌擦乾眼挫<br />\n<br />\n共同面對　化無理成灰<br />\n<br />\n誰失去理性百萬沒去聽<br />\n從不反省　全城噓聲<br />\n同暴政說不講句要自由帶領 離開險境<br />\n來反抗惡政拼盡力戰勝<br />\n狼死黑警    棍棍心驚<br />\n洋紫荊再花開你我共同見證<br />\n民主終會獲勝<br />\n<br />\n小弟中文一啲都唔好 希望大家唔好介意<br />\nWho will join in our crusade? Who will be strong and stand with me?<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">加油</span></span>"},{"pid":"dca37222f2a052e519f5fe1279b3b681ef31afb6","tid":1229234,"uid":261040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T00:42:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27509e30d2e65f68d2c68c3b11526346da589c97","tid":1229234,"uid":261040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T00:49:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b00d9bae7ff338de6436517f0d6a4df67dc89a5","tid":1229234,"uid":261040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T01:00:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab7dd594caf7aa43913163c1007ac080606aebc6","tid":1229234,"uid":162421,"like":0,"di